These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, social-worker
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, mexican
2 different pets are kept: turtle, rat
1. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the musician is on the right of the social-worker##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk      | fanta    |
| Job           | social-worker | musician |
| Nationality   | italian       | mexican  |
| Pet     | turtle      | rat     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, watermelon
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, magic-tricks
2 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | watermelon | cauliflower |
| Hobby   | chess       | magic-tricks         |
| Pet           | rabbit     | cat         |
| Transport     | scooter    | airplane    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, hiking
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, project-manager
2 different pets are kept: goat, dog
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter
1. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | hiking          | board-games |
| Job           | project-manager | analyst     |
| Pet   | goat            | dog         |
| Transport     | scooter         | quad-bike   |

